\c 12
\s Ukukhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* kumele kube sendaweni eyodwa
\p
\v 1 Lezi yizimiso lezahlulelo elizananzelela ukuzenza elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, ekunika lona ukuthi udle ilifa lalo\x + 6.1.\x*, zonke izinsuku eliphila ngazo emhlabeni\x + 4.10. 1 Kho. 8.40.\x*.
\v 2 Lizadiliza lokudiliza zonke indawo lapho izizwe elizazixotsha elifeni lazo ezazikhonzela khona onkulunkulu bazo, entabeni eziphakemeyo lemaqaqeni langaphansi kwaso sonke isihlahla esiluhlaza\x + 1 Kho. 14.23. 2 Kho. 16.4. 17.10. Jer. 3.6.\x*;
\v 3 lizadiliza amalathi azo, libulale insika zazo eziyizithombe, litshise izixuku zazo ngomlilo\x + Eks. 23.24.\x*, liqumele phansi izithombe ezibaziweyo zabonkulunkulu bazo, lichithe ibizo lazo kuleyondawo\x + 7.5.\x*.
\v 4 Lingenzi njalo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 12.31.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kodwa endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ezayikhetha phakathi kwazo zonke izizwe zenu ukubeka ibizo layo khona, lizadinga kundawo yayo yokuhlala; njalo uzakuya khona\x + 12.11,14,18,21,26. Dute. 14.23,24,25. 15.20. 16.2,6,7,11,15,16. 17.8. 18.6. 26.2. 31.11. Josh. 9.27. 1 Kho. 8.29. 2 Lan. 7.12. Hlab. 78.68. Josh. 18.1.\x*,
\v 6 lilethe khona iminikelo yenu yokutshiswa, lemihlatshelo yenu, lokwetshumi kwenu, lomnikelo wokuphakanyiswa wesandla senu, lezithembiso zenu, leminikelo yenu yesihle\x + 12.11,17. Dute. 14.22,23.\x*, lamazibulo enkomo zenu lawezimvu zenu\x + 14.23. 15.19,20.\x*;
\v 7 lidle khona phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 12.18. Dute. 14.26.\x*, lithokoze\x + 12.12,18. Levi 23.40. Dute. 14.26. 16.11,14,15. 26.11. 27.7.\x* ngakho konke elibeke isandla senu kukho, lina labendlu yenu, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekubusise ngakho\x + 12.18. Dute. 15.10. 23.20. 28.8,20.\x*.
\v 8 Kaliyikwenza njengakho konke esikwenzayo lapha lamuhla, ngulowo lalowo loba yikuphi okulungileyo emehlweni akhe\x + Hlu. 17.6. 21.25.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba kalikafiki ekuphumuleni lelifeni, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona.
\v 10 Lapho selichaphile iJordani, selihlezi elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elinika lona libe yilifa lenu, isiliphumuzile ezitheni zenu zonke inhlangothi zonke, selihlezi livikelekile\x + 11.31.\x*,
\v 11 khona kuzakuba lendawo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ezayikhetha ukwenza ibizo layo lihlale lapho\x + 12.5.\x*; lizaletha lapho konke engililaya khona, iminikelo yenu yokutshiswa, lemihlatshelo yenu, lokwetshumi kwenu, lomnikelo wokuphakanyiswa wesandla senu, lezithembiso zenu zonke ezikhethekileyo elizazithembisa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 12 Njalo lizathaba phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, lina lamadodana enu lamadodakazi enu, lenceku zenu lencekukazi zenu, lomLevi ophakathi kwamasango enu\x + 12.7.\x*, ngoba engelasabelo lelifa lani\x + Nani 18.20.\x*.
\v 13 Ziqaphele ukuthi unganikeli iminikelo yakho yokutshiswa kuyo yonke indawo oyibonayo\x + Levi 17.4.\x*;
\v 14 kodwa endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha kwesinye sezizwe zakho, lapho uzanikela iminikelo yakho yokutshiswa, lalapho uzakwenza konke engikulaya khona\x + 12.5,6.\x*.
\v 15 Kanti ungahlaba udle inyama, phakathi kwawo wonke amasango akho, njengaso sonke isifiso somphefumulo wakho, njengokwesibusiso seN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ekunike sona\x + 12.21.\x*; ongahlambulukanga lohlambulukileyo angakudla\x + 12.22.\x*, njengomziki lanjengendluzele\x + 14.5. 15.22. 1 Kho. 4.23.\x*.
\v 16 Kuphela lingadli igazi; lizalichithela emhlabathini njengamanzi\x + Levi 3.17.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Awulakudlela emasangweni akho okwetshumi kwamabele akho leyewayini lakho elitsha, leyamafutha akho, loba amazibulo enkomo zakho lawezimvu zakho, loba yikuphi kwesithembiso sakho osithembisileyo, loba iminikelo yakho yesihle, loba umnikelo wokuphakanyiswa wesandla sakho.
\v 18 Kodwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho uzadlela lokho endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha, wena lendodana yakho lendodakazi yakho, lenceku yakho lencekukazi yakho, lomLevi ophakathi kwamasango akho; njalo uzathaba phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 12.11,12. Dute. 14.23.\x* kukho konke obeka isandla sakho kukho\x + 12.18. Dute. 15.10. 23.20. 28.8,20.\x*.
\v 19 Ziqaphele ukuthi ungamkhohlwa umLevi zonke izinsuku zakho elizweni lakho\x + 14.27.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iqhelisa umngcele wakho, njengokukhuluma kwayo kuwe, njalo uzakuthi: Ngizakudla inyama, ngoba umphefumulo wakho ukhanuka ukudla inyama\x + Eks. 34.24. Dute. 19.8. Gen. 28.14. Dute. 11.24. 19.9.\x*; njengokwesifiso sonke somphefumulo wakho uzakudla inyama\x + 12.15.\x*.
\v 21 Uba indawo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ezayikhetha ukubeka ibizo layo khona ikhatshana lawe, uzahlaba enkomeni zakho loba ezimvini zakho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekunike zona, njengokukulaya kwami, uzakudlela phakathi kwamasango akho, njengokwesifiso sonke somphefumulo wakho\x + 12.15.\x*.
\v 22 Ngitsho, njengalokhu kudliwa umziki lendluzele, ngokunjalo uzazidla; ongahlambulukanga lohlambulukileyo angazidla ngokufananayo\x + 12.15.\x*.
\v 23 Kuphela qaphela ukuthi ungadli igazi\x + 12.16.\x*, ngoba igazi liyimpilo; ngakho kawuyikudla impilo kanye lenyama\x + Gen. 9.4.\x*.
\v 24 Ungalidli, uzalichithela emhlabathini njengamanzi.
\v 25 Ungalidli, ukuze kukulungele labantwana bakho emva kwakho\x + 4.40. Tshu. 8.12. Isa. 3.10.\x*, lapho usenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 15.26. Dute. 13.18. 1 Kho. 11.38.\x*\nd*.
\v 26 Kuphela izinto ezingcwele olazo\x + Nani 5.9,10. 18.19.\x*, lezithembiso zakho, uzazithatha, uye endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha\x + 1 Sam. 1.21.\x*.
\v 27 Ulungise iminikelo yakho yokutshiswa, inyama legazi, phezu kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho. Legazi lemihlatshelo yakho lizathululelwa phezu kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, lenyama ungayidla\x + Levi 1.5,9,13. 17.11.\x*.
\v 28 Qaphela uzwe wonke amazwi la engikulaya wona, ukuze kukulungele labantwana bakho emva kwakho kuze kube nininini, lapho usenza okulungileyo lokuqondileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 12.25.\x*.
\s Isixwayiso ngokukhonza abanye onkulunkulu
\p
\v 29 Lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izaquma izizwe zisuke phambi kwakho lapho oya khona ukudla ilifa lazo, lapho usudle ilifa lazo wahlala elizweni lazo\x + 19.1\x*,
\v 30 ziqaphele ukuthi ungathiywa uzilandele, emva kokuchithwa kwazo phambi kwakho, lokuthi ungabuzi ngonkulunkulu bazo usithi: Izizwe lezi zazikhonza njani onkulunkulu bazo? Lami ngizakwenza njalo\x + 7.16.\x*.
\v 31 Kawuyikwenza njalo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho; ngoba konke okunengekayo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ekuzondayo, zikwenzile kubonkulunkulu bazo\x + 12.4; Levi 18.3,25,26,30. 2 Kho. 17.15.\x*; ngoba ngitsho amadodana azo lamadodakazi azo zibatshisile ngomlilo kubonkulunkulu bazo.
\v 32 Yonke into engililaya ngayo, qaphelani ukuyenza; ungengezeleli kuyo, futhi ungaphunguli kuyo\x + 18.21\x*.